Package: ExactVaRTest
Title: Exact Finite-Sample VaR Back-Testing
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-07-15
Authors@R:
    person("Yujian", "Chen",
           email = "yjc4996@gmail.com",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides fast dynamic programming (forward) algorithms for the exact
    finite-sample distribution and p-values of Christoffersen's (1998)
    independence (IND) and conditional-coverage (CC) tests for
    Value-at-Risk (VaR) exception series.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    stats,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/YujianCHEN219/ExactVaRTest
BugReports: https://github.com/YujianCHEN219/ExactVaRTest/issues
Acknowledgements: |
